_sText:
This is a remake of the map dm17 from Quake3 Arena. Custom textures, ingame music (guess what, music from Q3A) and of course many teleports. A must have for any Quake 3 lover. It is recommended that you play with 10 players max but it can support as many players as you want. Only for the Deathmatch plug-in. It won't work nice on standard servers. 

Note that there is a "haste" powerup like in Q3A.


***EDIT***

Just this :D .

Hope you enjoy it!
